text: 50/50 is a 2011 American black comedy-drama movie directed by Jonathan Levine and written by Will Reiser. It stars Joseph Gordon-Levitt, Seth Rogen, Anna Kendrick, Bryce Dallas Howard, and Anjelica Huston with Philip Baker Hall. 50/50 was released on September 30, 2011. It made $41 million at the box office. It had strong positive reviews when it was released. ==References== Category:2011 comedy-drama movies Category:2010s black comedy movies Category:American black comedy movies Category:2010s English-language movies Category:Movies about death
